Name: Hentai Packer
About the game: Pack sexy girl called Lucy into tight spaces in this high quality puzzle game. Featuring polished and fun gameplay, and very high quality CG renders. Features: High quality CG renders of Lucy 30 levels of increasing difficulty Very fun and polished gameplay. Spicy image on each game tile as well as full renders available in the gallery Increasing difficulty from absolutely trivial to challenging. Different levels with different tiles, obstacles and game area size Your goal is to fit all the tiles into the game area, avoiding possible obstacles. You can drag and drop tiles and rotate them in space. Each level you will unlock new tiles with various shapes and images. The game escalates in complexity, in the first levels you will learn how to play (no boring tutorial needed) and in the later levels you will scratch your head and ponder!
